<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152485>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, holotype, male (36.7 × 28.5 mm) (ZRC 2023.0411), Thailand.A, overall dorsal habitus; B, dorsal view of carapace; C, frontal view of cephalothorax; D, antennules, antennae and epistome; E, chelae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152485/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152487>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, holotype, male (36.7 × 28.5 mm) (ZRC 2023.0411), Thailand. A, anterior half of thoracic sternum; B, posterior half of thoracic sternum and pleon; C, median part of thoracic sternum and pleon; D, sternopleonal cavity." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152487/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152489>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, holotype, male (36.7 × 28.5 mm) (ZRC 2023.0411), Thailand.A, left G1 (dorsal view); B, left G1 (ventral view); C, left G1 terminal segment (dorsal view); D, left G1 terminal segment (ventral view); E, left G2; F, left third maxilliped. Scale bar = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152489/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152491>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, paratype, female (27.5 × 21.5 mm) (ZRC 2023.0415), Thailand. A, overall dorsal habitus; B, pleon; C, sternopleonal cavity showing vulvae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152491/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152493>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, paratype, male (30.1 × 24.0 mm) (ZRC 2023.0412), Thailand.A, overall dorsal habitus; B, anterior thoracic sternum and pleon; C, frontal view of cephalothorax; D, antennules, antennae and epistome." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152495>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Live colouration. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, male, not preserved, Thailand. A, overall dorsal habitus; B, overall ventral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10152495/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10152497>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Map of Isthmus of Kra, inset map showing collection points of Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, in red points." ;
